Mini cottage w/ free parking.

This small cottage is located in our beautiful backyard. It is close to everything. A 15 min drive to downtown San Francisco and SF airport. A 15 min walk to Westlake shopping center and Bart station to San Francisco. The beautiful unit has a private entrance, one bedroom with a queen bed and a private bathroom. 
We provide Wi-fi, towels, instant coffee, tea, and snack. More amenities for you to use: TV, microwave,  refrigerator, hair dryer & electric kettle.


Our beautiful backyard.
